BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 70.08000000000001 600 Td (Chapter 9: Decluttering Paper and Mail) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Paper clutter is one of the most common and most stressful forms of clutter.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Immediately recycle junk mail at the door before it enters your living space.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Unsubscribe from catalogs and switch to paperless billing for all accounts.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Shred documents with personal information before recycling them.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Keep only: tax documents \(7 years\), vital records, active insurance policies.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Create a simple filing system: Action, Reference, and Archive categories.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Action holds items needing response: bills to pay, forms to complete.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Process the Action folder weekly so it never becomes an overwhelming pile.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Scan important documents and store digital copies as backup.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Children's artwork can be photographed and then rotate a few displayed pieces.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Designate one spot as the paper landing zone and process it weekly.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Once you control paper flow, your surfaces stay clear with minimal effort.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 213.6 30 Td (9) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
