BT 0 g /F2 16 Tf 93.12 600 Td (Chapter 10: Digital Decluttering) Tj ET
q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Digital clutter causes the same mental fog as physical clutter in your space.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Unsubscribe from email newsletters you never read using unroll.me or manually.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Delete apps you have not opened in the last thirty days from your phone.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Organize your phone home screen to show only apps you use daily.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Delete blurry, duplicate, and unflattering photos from your camera roll.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Organize remaining photos into albums by year or event for easy finding.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Clear your computer desktop by filing documents into organized folders.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Empty your downloads folder which likely contains hundreds of forgotten files.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Review and delete old bookmarks, saved articles you will never read, and dead links.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Organize your files into a simple folder structure: Work, Personal, Finance.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Turn off non-essential notifications that interrupt your focus throughout the day.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (A clean digital environment reduces decision fatigue just like a clean room.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F1 10 Tf 211.2 30 Td (10) Tj ET

endstream
endobj
