q 0 G 1 w 60 585 m 372 585 l S Q
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 560 Td (Day 1: Declutter your wallet or purse. Remove old receipts and expired cards.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 538 Td (Day 2: Clear one kitchen drawer completely. Keep only daily-use items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 516 Td (Day 3: Go through your medicine cabinet. Discard expired items.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 494 Td (Day 4: Unsubscribe from 10 email newsletters you never read.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 472 Td (Day 5: Declutter your car. Remove trash, unused items, and unnecessary weight.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 450 Td (Day 6: Tackle one closet shelf. Remove items you have not used in a year.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 428 Td (Day 7: Clear your nightstand. Keep only sleep-related essentials.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 406 Td (Day 8: Declutter kitchen countertops. Store or donate counter appliances rarely used.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 384 Td (Day 9: Go through your book collection. Donate books you will not reread.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 362 Td (Day 10: Delete 50 photos from your phone that are blurry or duplicates.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 340 Td (Days 11-20: Tackle one room per day using the 4-box method for 30 minutes.) Tj ET
BT 0 g /F4 11 Tf 50 318 Td (Days 21-30: Maintain what you have cleared and do one final sweep of each space.) Tj ET
